"pid":"8a8815f59047eed9e53c480340c28f57b36de808","tid":1517444,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"泛民其實都有好多好人架，希望班黑警唔好拉鳩佢地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時我地冇大台真係唔知點算架會，嗚嗚嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c9b2574eef46580d11cb8820e28eacc15449c8","tid":1517444,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"一人一個名要求警察支持嚴正執法"},{"pid":"20ef0bd5f37b0373dfa2813c4fe5f38eaebc0bd9","tid":1517444,"uid":263114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"大家唔好唔記得我地仲有燒山呢個大台係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266e206d6ed5f3625aec34c969fb57dafc88b76a","tid":1517444,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:52:14.000Z","msg":"拉埋林鄭<br />\n係佢搞出黎"},{"pid":"22897aba3aa181a63e5376cdc30fc80dd6f8a046","tid":1517444,"uid":264074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩黑警冇拉泛民, 如果唔係場運動一定會散啦!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6270bddb3a2bf1372a572408eaa563e3ad54fca5","tid":1517444,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df9a42863f0a82c50320736d84987555bebb486d","tid":1517444,"uid":141151,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:33:37.000Z","msg":"何式凝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T03:02:13.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人被販民出賣了</span></span><br />\n販民不是反送中運動大台，但是，販民在美國議員面前扮大台。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">販民和建制跑去美國和美國國會議員開「閉門會議」表示建制和販民達成協議，示威者得到滿意回應，反送中運動和平結束。今天楊某收到美國吹來的風，建制販民在閉門會議向美國議員表示販民已經達到共識，反送中示威和平結束。</span></span><br />\n今日，黃之鋒和陳浩天被捕，岑子杰遇襲。林賤企圖以大規模拘捕行動瓦解示威組織，拘捕和打擊所有示威組織知名人士，包括申請示威的攪手讓反送中示威平靜下來。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美國人就會相信反送中示威完結，美國人可以收工。</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">看吧，這幾天，美國議員全部靜下來，沒有發表支持香港反送中言論。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">販民已經淪為港共政治工具，為港共效力，替林賤消愁解困。建制販民可能已經安排日後成立假自治政治，分豬肉式撈好處。香港人被販民出賣了。</span>"},{"pid":"0ed2147796237f180cccde155b4b1cf732d2ee5f","tid":1517444,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d47654cf7f793b4c5adaaebbeec7048c7a0eb1","tid":1517444,"uid":191527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72761d7f52c0f393216be8b3f9e7792872328804","tid":1517444,"uid":4285,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"係，呢件友七一係好前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:36:28.000Z","msg":"順手拉埋你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:38:46.000Z","msg":"如果鳩逹都拉，個濫捕情況係超嚴重 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔出街都拉"},{"pid":"f673581d3957f58174ccc1b54b69f39ec358cfff","tid":1517444,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0ed2147796237f180cccde155b4b1cf732d2ee5f","tid":1517444,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86d47654cf7f793b4c5adaaebbeec7048c7a0eb1","tid":1517444,"uid":191527,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72761d7f52c0f393216be8b3f9e7792872328804","tid":1517444,"uid":4285,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"係，呢件友七一係好前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,